    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so you won\u2019t find a single blemish or weird noise anywhere. It\u2019s been super reliable and drives like a cloud. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one! Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
